label.phrase: and the house had burned down that day they'd just had a significant house fire and with tony you know he would tell you that happened but it absolutely didn't affect his enjoyment of the evening or his outlook on life a lot of us would you know really be bummed out if we just had a major house fire and he had this capacity to sort of put everything in its place maintain his perspective and i think he'd want us to do that now i think he lived his life to the fullest
